79
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:57,040
I just don't have confidence in this city.

80
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,800
If I stay here,

81
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,710
I worry that I'll lose every last bit of self-dignity I have.

82
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:06,560
It couldn't be that bad.

83
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:10,700
Do you know why I didn't go work for President Guo?

84
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:17,230
It's because I'm petty, I'm narrow-minded.

85
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:19,660
I kept doubting for no reason,

86
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:22,130
