87
00:08:22,930 --> 00:08:25,060
Because I feel inferior.

88
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:28,540
And I'm scared of losing you.

89
00:08:30,890 --> 00:08:34,940
I really hate... I really loathe resigning like this.

90
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:38,450
But if I stay in Shanghai,

91
00:08:39,340 --> 00:08:42,730
